# Admin portal build gate

Before committing any change under `admin-portal/`:

1. Run `npm run build` from the `admin-portal/` directory.
2. Fix all TypeScript and build errors before staging or committing.
3. Do not push admin-portal changes if the production build fails locally.

Vercel runs `next build` on deploy; a passing local build prevents failed deployments.
